<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Dec 2021 11:56:03 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>EVA 新精品登陸 7-Eleven  新色收納箱 + 手機充電器</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/28/7-eleven-3/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=7-eleven-3</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 28 Dec 2021 11:43:11 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活娛樂]]></category><category><![CDATA[生活評測]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078557</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>今期 7-Eleven 預購站聯乘人氣動漫 Evangelion 新世紀福音戰士，新推出 NERV 總部黑色可 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>今期 7-Eleven 預購站聯乘人氣動漫 Evangelion 新世紀福音戰士，新推出 NERV 總部黑色可疊存儲物箱和外置充電器 ，並再次預售初號機紫色可疊存儲物箱，將家居雜物通通收妥。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01847.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078595" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01847-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01847-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01847-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01847.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01853.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01853-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01853-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01853-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01853.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>EVA「緊急外部電源」流動電源</h2><p>Evangelion 外置充電器擁有鮮紅色的外型，背面更印有緊急外部電源字眼，非常搶眼亦型格十足。機身輕便易攜，方便外出使用。外部電源設有 4 個電池顯示燈，內置高容量 5000mAh 電池，有 USB 充電接口及 Type-C 充電線，隨時隨地為通訊設備補給電量。預購價為港幣$229。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01863.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01863-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01863-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01863-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01863.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01866.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078563" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01866-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01866-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01866-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01866.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲充電器背面印上「緊急外部電源」字樣</p><h2>預購價：港幣$229</h2><h2>「非常事態」收納箱</h2><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01831.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01831-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01831-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01831-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01831.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>除實用又精美的初號機儲物箱再度登場，是次全新推出黑紅配色的儲物箱，適合型格家居。儲物箱安裝方便，立起儲物箱後打開盒頂，把內置的兩塊側板放下拍緊，便完成安裝。儲物箱更可疊高使用，具大容量的儲物空間，方便各位整頓裝備。不使用時亦可摺疊收納，不佔空間，家居雜物一秒隱藏，兩款儲物箱預購價皆為港幣$250。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01792.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01792-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01792-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01792-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01792.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01799-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078576" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01799-1-694x456.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="456" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01799-1-694x456.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01799-1-768x504.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01799-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01813.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078581" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01813-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01813-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01813-768x480.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01813.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01838-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078579" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01838-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01838-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01838-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC01838-2.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>預購價：港幣$250</h2><p>此預購只適用於香港及澳門 7-Eleven 店舖，每單交易只限預購 1 件，有意購買者可於 2021 年 12 月 29 日早上 7 時起至 2022 年 1 月 11 日到點撃進入 7-Eleven 預購站 <a href="http://www.7-eleven.com.hk/zh/news/preorder">www.7-eleven.com.hk/zh/news/preorder</a> 預購。</p><div></div><div class="css-kl86x4">資料來源：7-Eleven</div><div></div><div class="css-kl86x4">—</div><div class="css-16zmdoi" data-is-focusable="true">unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></div></p><div class="feedflare">
